content.rendered:
Directed by Trinadha Rao Nakkina

Written by Prasanna Kumar Bezawada. Trinadha Rao Nakkina

Cast Ravi Teja (Swami / Anand Chakravarthy). Sreeleela (Pranavi Reddy). Jayaram (JP). Sachin Khedekar (Nanda Gopal Chakravarthy). Tanikella Bharani (Vasudeva Rao). Rao Ramesh (Ramesh Reddy). Chirag Jani (Atharva).Hyper Adhi. Mohammad Ali (JP’s worker). Pavitra Lokesh (Devaki).Rajshri Nair.Praveen. Tulasi (Yashoda)

Languages Telugu

Producers Sujith Kumar Kolli. Vivek Kuchibhotla. T.G. Vishwa Prasad

Production People Media Factory.. Abhishek Aggarwal Arts. B4U Motion Pictures
